title: egomio
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This Greek taverna has a vegetarian section on their menu. Vegan options include vegetable soup, pasta napolitan, stuffed vegetables, stuffed aubergine (eggplant), veg mousaka, vine leaves and more. You may want to make sure your order is without cheese or tzaziki (yogurt). Wi-fi.
streetAddress: Street of the port Livadia, Parikia
